<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4450525>
    dc:description "FIGURE 2. Synergus aurofacies, sp. nov.: a) female habitus; b) male habitus; c) female face; d) male face; e) first antennal segments of the male; f) female forewing; g) host gall." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4450525/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4450527>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Synergus aurofacies, sp. nov.: a) female head in frontal view; b) female head in dorsal view; c) mesosoma in lateral view (the black arrow points out the speculum); d) mesosoma in dorsal view; e) tarsal claws; f) female antenna; g) propodeum; h) metasoma in lateral view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4450527/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4450523>
    dc:description "FIGURE 1. Synergus agrifoliae: a) female lateral habitus; b) female dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4450523/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4450529>
    dc:description "FIGURE 4. Synergus campanula: a) lateral habitus; b) dorsal view. Synergus confertus: c) lateral habitus; d) dorsal view. Synergus flavens: e) lateral habitus; f) dorsal view. Synergus laeviventris: g) lateral habitus; h) dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4450529/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.4450533>
    dc:description "FIGURE 5. Synergus profusus (synonym of S. pacificus): a) lateral habitus; b) dorsal view. Synergus pomiformis: c) lateral habitus; d) dorsal view. Synergus succinipedis: e) lateral habitus; f) dorsal view." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/4450533/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

